Package: MettleRNASeq
Title: Machine-Learning-Assisted Analysis of Complex RNA-Seq Datasets
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Samella",
        family = "Salles",
        email = "ssalles@posgrad.lncc.br",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5521-4717")
    )
)
Description: Provides tools for machine-learning-assisted analysis of
    complex RNA-seq datasets, especially when traditional differential gene
    expression analysis is limited by small sample size, high variability, or
    complex biological mechanisms. MettleRNASeq integrates data preparation,
    principal component analysis, feature selection, tailored classification,
    correlation analysis, and association rule mining to identify
    discriminative genes and explore gene relationships across experimental
    conditions.
